      "display_name": "no parent but duplicate",
      "connector_key": "ai",
      "action_key": "generic_ai",
      "input_config": {
        "control": "object",
        "value": {
          "output_format": {
            "control": "picklist",
            "value": "markdown"
          },
          "user_prompt": {
            "control": "text",
            "value": "Summary banner\n\nYellow (if vendors are similar):\nRed (if vendors are exact match): \n- Title: \"Potential duplicate vendor found\" if single or if multiple \"Potential duplicate vendors found\"\n- Subtext: Below are the similar vendors found to \"${steps.zip_1.vendor.name}\"\n\nHeader: \"Similar vendors\"\n\nFor each VISIBLE candidate list the following data if present:\n\n# Header: \"<Vendor name>\" Include citation linking to the vendor \n- Legal name\n- Email domain\n- Alternate name (DBA)\n- Created: \n- Country\n- Subsidiaries this vendor works with:\n\nHeader: \"Next steps\"\n\nRecommendation section\nTitle: Double check this vendor\nDescription: If one of the vendors listed matches the vendor you’re trying to create, update your request to use the existing vendor. Output here is limited to just the four most similar vendors.\n=========\n\nbelow are the similar vendors found\n${steps.ai_2.response}\n"
          },
          "tools": {
            "control": "multipicklist",
            "value": [
              "zip_data"
            ]
          },
          "include_citations": {
            "control": "boolean",
            "value": true
          },
