            "value": "Summary banner\n\nYellow (if vendors are similar):\nRed (if vendors are exact match): \n- Title: \"Potential duplicate vendor found\" if single or if multiple \"Potential duplicate vendors found\"\n- Subtext: Below are the similar vendors found to \"${steps.zip_1.vendor.name}\"\n\n\nHeader \"Parent company\"\n\n# Header: \"<Vendor name>\" (Include citation linking to the vendor)\n- Legal name\n- Email domain\n- Alternate name (DBA)\n- Created: \n- Country\n- Subsidiaries this vendor works with:\n\nHeader: \"Similar vendors\" (only render this if similar vendors is different from parent company)\n\nFor each VISIBLE candidate list the following data if present:\n\n# Header: \"<Vendor name>\" (Include citation linking to the vendor)\n- Legal name\n- Email domain\n- Alternate name (DBA)\n- Created: \n- Country\n- Subsidiaries this vendor works with:\n\nHeader: \"Next steps\"\n\n(Recommendation section)\n\nTitle: Double check this vendor\nDescription: We found vendor records in your system that match \"${steps.zip_1.vendor.name}\", and we also identified a related parent company. Please review the matches before proceeding with creating or updating this vendor.\n\n=========\n\nbelow are the similar vendors found\n${steps.ai_2.response}\n\nparent company info:\n${steps.ai_4.response.parentInfo}"
